        Getting Started
        -----------------
        
        - Begin from here:
        --./setup.py
        
        -----------------
        client:
        ```
        from nameko.standalone.rpc import ClusterRpcProxy
        with ClusterRpcProxy({"AMQP_URI":"amqp://guest:guest@localhost"}) as cli:
        	result = cli.user_service.add(conn_id='10', user_name='', email="x@y", role='')
        ```
        
        
        
